title: Do You Believe Jussie Smollett
itunes:title: Do You Believe Jussie Smollett
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines after news got out that Jussie Smollett charges were dropped, so we wanted to know if any of our listeners still believe that he is guilty of the crime. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a drunk driver that sprayed axe in his mouth in hopes to fool cop and Angela helped some listeners out during Ask Yee.
